{"tid":1868653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢個武漢Youtuber，妻子為急診室護士，確診感染武漢肺炎，居然不用入院而係在家自行隔離","createTime":"2020-02-07T16:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T17:05:55.000Z","uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"117e558eaec0a68e1d3bab870434007f9e6b42a0","tid":1868653,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"他的妻子係1月底確診，但醫生話病情不嚴重，所以竟然叫他妻子在家隔離！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gstvtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gstvtd.jpg&h=16ddf935&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n所謂在家隔離，其實只係在一間普通的睡房。丈夫每日穿戴防護衣入去照顧妻子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETrh8eC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETrh8eC.jpg&h=b133db9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCT中已經可以見到成團的病毒！而咁樣的病情，醫生居然容許在家隔離！<br />\n<br />\n雖然夫妻情深、令人感動，但咁樣任由確診患者係社區生活，太大風險了！咁樣做，疫情點會受控呢？根本係一個定時炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CbXyHGrXAsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCbXyHGrXAsY&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=8b6caa1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CbXyHGrXAsY</a>"},{"pid":"59e822c777a263d3e1a53bc9746a9d80d0991858","tid":1868653,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPv61Bp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPv61Bp.jpg&h=cbdfaf5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d02f3f7240311951daab01680b2fcffaa759cd5e","tid":1868653,"uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"因為佢知道入院，小事變大事"},{"pid":"dfb1e8b902b1735b14d336dc6de0c591e0820d9f","tid":1868653,"uid":64956,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"一齊住都好易感染啦"},{"pid":"22ff0aad599f54361970b5506596c681e621d6d1","tid":1868653,"uid":326017,"like":0,"